The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as Neural Architectural Search (NAS) and Progressive Search, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). 

Additionally, the paper involves optimizing for device-related objectives such as inference time and memory usage, which falls under the sub-categories of Neural Engineering (cs.NE) and Architecture (cs.AR).
